{"word":"G3569 - τανῦν - tanŷn - tan-oon' - Now","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τανῦν</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">tanŷn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">tan-oon'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Now</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இப்பொழுது - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"now, at present"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From neuter plural of <a href=\"#/G3588 - ὁ - ho - ho/3588\">G3588</a> and <a href=\"#/G3568 - νῦν - nŷn - noon/3568\">G3568</a>; <i>the</i> things <i>now</i>, that is, (adverb) <i>at present:</i> - (but) now.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3568/3568\">G3568</a>, <a href=\"#/G3569/3569\">G3569</a>, <a href=\"#/G3570/3570\">G3570</a>"}]}